  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285940/extras/0d78c3a6abd63e610169ffb6a33b4e24.avif?t=1757097525\" width=600 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hollow Survivors</strong> is a rogue-like dungeon crawler where you play as one of the few remaining sane Hollows. Slash through hordes of <i>horrific</i> creatures and fight your way to the <i>top of the Tower</i>. Discover new weapons and upgrades, and confront the evil cult that turned you into a Hollow. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285940/extras/769b89ccc58b5c704e293af239dba2c3.poster.avif?t=1757097525\" width=600 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285940/extras/769b89ccc58b5c704e293af239dba2c3.webm?t=1757097525\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285940/extras/769b89ccc58b5c704e293af239dba2c3.mp4?t=1757097525\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FACE POWERFUL ENEMIES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unleash your fury, <strong>crush your enemies</strong> and triumph over <strong>menacing bosses</strong> that stand in your path. Nothing can stop you from achieving your goal.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285940/extras/7f955e0dfa0b9e9f802ebe709ad22813.poster.avif?t=1757097525\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285940/extras/7f955e0dfa0b9e9f802ebe709ad22813.webm?t=1757097525\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285940/extras/7f955e0dfa0b9e9f802ebe709ad22813.mp4?t=1757097525\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CHOOSE YOUR WEAPON</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pick a weapon that best suits your combat style. Use a <strong>swift scythe</strong> to quickly cut down your enemies or wield a <strong>great axe</strong> to overwhelm them with power.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285940/extras/c90e67a0c227fc57c0a10d89cdabb32f.poster.avif?t=1757097525\" width=600 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285940/extras/c90e67a0c227fc57c0a10d89cdabb32f.webm?t=1757097525\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285940/extras/c90e67a0c227fc57c0a10d89cdabb32f.mp4?t=1757097525\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GROW STRONGER</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Death is not the end in Hollow Survivors. Utilize the souls you gather to purchase <strong>permanent upgrades</strong> from other Hollows, ensuring that you grow stronger with each run.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285940/extras/415a2c98d51e1b3c62769136c6fe870b.poster.avif?t=1757097525\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285940/extras/415a2c98d51e1b3c62769136c6fe870b.webm?t=1757097525\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285940/extras/415a2c98d51e1b3c62769136c6fe870b.mp4?t=1757097525\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BEFRIEND OTHER HOLLOWS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grow your <strong>relationships</strong> with other Hollows, uncover dark secrets, and <strong>rebuild</strong> the settlement.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285940/extras/69ceb1b6f52c27dfd56d1beb5e826938.poster.avif?t=1757097525\" width=600 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285940/extras/69ceb1b6f52c27dfd56d1beb5e826938.webm?t=1757097525\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285940/extras/69ceb1b6f52c27dfd56d1beb5e826938.mp4?t=1757097525\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >UNIQUE BUILD = UNIQUE LOOK</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each soul-card you select directly influences your character's <i>appearance</i>. Every unique combination creates a distinct look for the player.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285940/extras/c20b0038585eefca0c2d70ab873e26b3.poster.avif?t=1757097525\" width=600 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285940/extras/c20b0038585eefca0c2d70ab873e26b3.webm?t=1757097525\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285940/extras/c20b0038585eefca0c2d70ab873e26b3.mp4?t=1757097525\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CUSTOMIZE YOUR CHARACTER</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Buy <strong>cosmetic upgrades</strong> to craft a unique look for your character. From subtle tweaks to dramatic transformations, you have the freedom to customize your hero exactly how you envision.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285940/extras/4544615fb5ece3b4ea12e1abdd77e63c.poster.avif?t=1757097525\" width=600 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285940/extras/4544615fb5ece3b4ea12e1abdd77e63c.webm?t=1757097525\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285940/extras/4544615fb5ece3b4ea12e1abdd77e63c.mp4?t=1757097525\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience an exciting action-packed adventure where your choices and skills determine your fate. <strong>Will you rise to the <i>ultimate test</i>?</strong></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285940/extras/0d78c3a6abd63e610169ffb6a33b4e24.avif?t=1757097525\" width=600 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hollow Survivors</strong> is a rogue-like dungeon crawler where you play as one of the few remaining sane Hollows. Slash through hordes of <i>horrific</i> creatures and fight your way to the <i>top of the Tower</i>. Discover new weapons and upgrades, and confront the evil cult that turned you into a Hollow. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285940/extras/769b89ccc58b5c704e293af239dba2c3.poster.avif?t=1757097525\" width=600 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285940/extras/769b89ccc58b5c704e293af239dba2c3.webm?t=1757097525\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285940/extras/769b89ccc58b5c704e293af239dba2c3.mp4?t=1757097525\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FACE POWERFUL ENEMIES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unleash your fury, <strong>crush your enemies</strong> and triumph over <strong>menacing bosses</strong> that stand in your path. Nothing can stop you from achieving your goal.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285940/extras/7f955e0dfa0b9e9f802ebe709ad22813.poster.avif?t=1757097525\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285940/extras/7f955e0dfa0b9e9f802ebe709ad22813.webm?t=1757097525\" type=\"video