4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BEFRIEND OTHER HOLLOWS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grow your <strong>relationships</strong> with other Hollows, uncover dark secrets, and <strong>rebuild</strong> the settlement.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285940/extras/69ceb1b6f52c27dfd56d1beb5e826938.poster.avif?t=1757097525\" width=600 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285940/extras/69ceb1b6f52c27dfd56d1beb5e826938.webm?t=1757097525\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285940/extras/69ceb1b6f52c27dfd56d1beb5e826938.mp4?t=1757097525\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >UNIQUE BUILD = UNIQUE LOOK</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each soul-card you select directly influences your character's <i>appearance</i>. Every unique combination creates a distinct look for the player.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285940/extras/c20b0038585eefca0c2d70ab873e26b3.poster.avif?t=1757097525\" width=600 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285940/extras/c20b0038585eefca0c2d70ab873e26b3.webm?t=1757097525\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285940/extras/c20b0038585eefca0c2d70ab873e26b3.mp4?t=1757097525\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CUSTOMIZE YOUR CHARACTER</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Buy <strong>cosmetic upgrades</strong> to craft a unique look for your character. From subtle tweaks to dramatic transformations, you have the freedom to customize your hero exactly how you envision.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285940/extras/4544615fb5ece3b4ea12e1abdd77e63c.poster.avif?t=1757097525\" width=600 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285940/extras/4544615fb5ece3b4ea12e1abdd77e63c.webm?t=1757097525\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285940/extras/4544615fb5ece3b4ea12e1abdd77e63c.mp4?t=1757097525\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience an exciting action-packed adventure where your choices and skills determine your fate. <strong>Will you rise to the <i>ultimate test</i>?</strong></p>",
